{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "暴雨清晨，楚留香感到强烈杀气，故意诱使伊贺第一忍者春雷伊次出刀，再以隐身般的压力反制，使其未交手便崩溃自尽。樱子传话邀他赴忘情馆，石田斋彦左卫门以明珠碧玉重金相诱，请他刺杀史天王。楚留香看穿其冷酷，借小情拒绝交易。夜里樱子潜入马车，追问他为何拒收石田斋的钱，并透露石田斋仇恨史天王是因爱妾霞姬被夺，自己曾混入玉剑山庄偷走公主。她又指出史天王常住“天王号”，愿助楚留香登船，楚留香表面温柔试探，最后把她抛出车厢。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_lin_zhong_tan_xi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "暗林中叹息的人",
      "listener": "char_chun_lei_yi_ci",
      "text": "你死了，你已经死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_lin_zhong_tan_xi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "暗林中叹息的人",
      "listener": "char_chun_lei_yi_ci",
      "text": "如果楚香帅也跟你一样是个杀人的人，那么你现在就已经是个死人了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_lin_zhong_tan_xi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "暗林中叹息的人",
      "listener": "char_chun_lei_yi_ci",
      "text": "我实在想不到号称无敌的伊贺第一忍者春雷伊次，这一次居然败得这么惨，楚香帅还没有出手，你就已败在他手里，实在太可惜。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚香帅，今夜掌灯时，有人会在忘情馆的情姑娘那里恭候香帅的大驾，我也希望香帅能去，却不知道香帅敢不敢去?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在下石田斋彦左卫门，虽然久居东瀛小国，却也久慕香帅的侠名。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "今日凌晨，在下更有幸能目睹香帅以无声无形无影的不动之剑，战胜了伊次势如春雷的刀法，使在下领悟了以静制动，以不变应万变的武艺妙谛，也使在下大开了眼界。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "石田斋先生真是太客气了，只可惜我是个不太会客气的人，而且有种病。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香帅也有病?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么病?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "头痛病。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "我一听见别人说客气话，就会头痛得要命!",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么我就直话直说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知不知道是谁要伊次去杀你的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "我知道，是你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我为什么要他去杀你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为我要知道你是不是真有传说中那么大的本事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "你为什么要知道这一点?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为我要你替我去杀一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "杀谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "史天王。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "你为什么要杀他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "为什么不留着他来对付我们?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我要杀他，只不过是我跟他私人之间的一点点恩怨而已。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我已经活得太久了，现在我活着惟一的愿望，就是希望能看到他比我先死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "要他死当然很不容易，惟一能做到这件事的人，可能就是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但是我也知道要你做这件事也同样不容易。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道她用三十万两买了口箱子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是我相信这口箱子大概还不止三十万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "这口箱子大概最少也要值一百五十万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "就算这是贼赃，拿去卖给收赃的人，也可以卖七八十万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香帅的眼光果然高明极了，只不过我估价的方法却和香帅有一点不一样。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "哪一点不一样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我是用人来估价的。我一向喜欢以人来估价。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我估计这口箱子大概已足够买到三千个黄花处子的贞操，也足够能买到同样多的勇士去替我拼命了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在这口箱子已经是你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "speaker_name": "石田斋彦左卫门",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如果你办成了我要你去办的那件事，另外还有一口同样的箱子也是你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qing",
      "text": "小情，你在哪里?你能不能进来一下?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qing",
      "text": "这口箱子里的东西最少值一百五十万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qing",
      "text": "要是这位老先生肯把这口箱子给你，你肯不肯陪他睡觉?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qing",
      "speaker_name": "小情",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我怎么会不肯?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qing",
      "speaker_name": "小情",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我做的本来就是这种事，做我们这种事的女人，一辈子都赚不了这么多，如果一天晚上就能赚这么多，不管叫我干什么都行。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qing",
      "speaker_name": "小情",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜今天晚上我恐怕没法子赚了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qing",
      "speaker_name": "小情",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为今天晚上有你在，我要陪你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "看起来，今天晚上你好像已经没有希望了，不管你是要找人陪你睡觉，还是要找人替你拼命，都没有希望了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "所以你最好还是走吧!带着你这口箱子走，而且最好快一点走。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_tian_zhai_yan_zuo_wei_men",
      "text": "因为我可以保证，明天晚上你恐怕也一样没有希望的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "不可以这样子，我会打你屁股的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我就知道你没有真的睡着，可是你如果再不睁开眼睛来，我说不定就要把你吃下去了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你能不能告诉我，为什么一定要把我吵醒?为什么不能让我睡一觉?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我睡不着，你也不能睡。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你为什么睡不着?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我有心事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你也有心事?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你怎么会有心事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为我听到了一些本来不应该听到的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你本来也不会让我听到这些话的，只可惜那天晚上你坐在屋顶上喝酒的时候，喝得太痛快了，竟忘了附近有个学过十七年忍术的女人，也跟你一样，是个偷听别人说话的专家。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "那天我们说的话你全都听见了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就因为我听见了，所以才奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你自己明明已决心要去找史天王，石田斋要你去的时候，你为什么反而要拒绝他?那是一百五十万两银子，可不是一百五十两，你为什么不收下来?难道你认为他的人太好了，不忍心拿他的银子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "也许是的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那你为什么又硬要从我这个可怜的女人身上弄走三十万两呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "因为你不但要偷看别人洗澡，而且还要把别人装到箱子里去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道你说的不是真话，你不肯收石田斋的银子，只不过因为你讨厌他那种人，不愿意替他做事而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如果你讨厌一个人，就算他把银子堆在你的面前，堆得比山还高，你也不会去看一眼的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "这么样说来，我既然肯要你的银子，当然是因为我喜欢你了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我也喜欢你，我比谁都喜欢你，当然也比那位公主更喜欢你，我也知道你喜欢我是假的，我喜欢你却一点不假。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是我实在不明白你是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "石田斋要对付史天王，只因为史天王抢去了他的爱妾霞姬，你呢?你为的是什么，难道真的是为了那位公主?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "史天王抢走了石田斋的爱妾，所以他才要你去偷史天王的公主，可是玉剑山庄里高手如云，你怎么能把她装进箱子偷走的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "三个月前我就想法子接替了香儿的差使。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香儿就是专门伺候公主洗澡的丫头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你大概也知道那位公主是个很喜欢干净的人。换下来的衣服很少再穿第二次，常常要我把一箱子一箱子的旧衣服拿出去送人。这已经不是第一次了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "只不过这一次你拿出来的那口箱子里装的不是旧衣服，而是穿衣服的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "听你说起来，这件事好像简单得很。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "本来就简单得很。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "世上有很多看起来很复杂困难的事，其实都是这么简单的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只不过如果有人想混上史天王那条名字叫做天王号的大海船，那就没有这么简单了，就算是无所不能的楚留香，恐怕也一样办不到。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "哦!",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个月里，他总有二十多天住在那条船上，如果你上不了那条船，就根本见不到他的人，如果你根本不知道船在哪里，怎么能上得了船?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "要做到这件事实在不简单。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "幸好问题还是可以解决的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不管多困难的事，总有法子可以解决。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "怎么解决?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你只要能找到一个有办法的人帮你的忙，问题就解决了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "谁是这个有办法的人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我!",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这个有办法的人就是我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "这么样看起来，我的运气好像还不错，居然能遇到你这么一个有办法的人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我早就听说你的运气一向都好得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "可是你为什么要帮我这个忙?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "第一，因为我高兴；第二，因为我愿意。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "第三，因为我喜欢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你怎么会忽然变得这么喜欢我的?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "是不是那位石田斋先生又花了几十万两银要你来喜欢我?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎么能这样子说话?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么总是要把我看成一个无情无义的女人?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "我知道你又有情，又有义，我也知道，如果没有你，这件事我是绝对办不成的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "可是你知不知道现在我最想做的一件事是什么事?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我真的不知道。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "我相信你非但不知道，而且连想都想不到。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "樱子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "也许我知道呢?我早就想到了呢!",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    }
  ],
